com.tjerkw.slideexpandable.library
Class ActionSlideExpandableListView

java.lang.Object
  ListView
      com.tjerkw.slideexpandable.library.ActionSlideExpandableListView

public class ActionSlideExpandableListView
extends ListView

A more specific expandable listview in which the expandable area consist of some buttons which are context actions for the item itself. It handles event binding for those buttons and allow for adding a listener that will be invoked if one of those buttons are pressed.

Author:
tjerk

enableExpandOnItemClick

public void enableExpandOnItemClick()
Registers a OnItemClickListener for this listview which will expand the item by default. Any other OnItemClickListener will be overriden. To undo call setOnItemClickListener(null) Important: This method call setOnItemClickListener, so the value will be reset
